snippet.title: College Kings - Act IV:  Part 1 [Play Now On Patreon]
snippet.description:
The waiting time is over.

College Kings Act IV: Part 1 is available now for all Senior patrons and all Junior+ Patrons with a total pledge of over $20.

San Vallejo is on fire!
Highly impactful choices, innovative gameplay, and much more.

PLAY NOW ON PATREON: https://www.patreon.com/collegekings/
Join the community: https://discord.collegekingsgame.com/
